message.body: When works for you to see my pretty face?
Hey! So I am getting breakfast with Fairleigh from 9:45-10:15, then I am free again at around 11:20ish, maybe 11:10, until 3. When are you eating lunch?
I was meeting Lizzie for lunch from 11-11:40 or so so you should come by at 11:20 or so and hang out on the DC!
Apparently I need to talk to you about housing. Remind me when I see you
